This was a old map I built a long time ago. I did some things to it to make it better - as you can see. It could be a bit dark as its a beta i was going to make the next one less dark and most likely have better/more effects in.
Hope you like it. 
Also there are some other things that I will need to fix in the next version. Like the sun is in the wrong place for the skybox.

Good luck. Have fun. 

Sorry about my graphics not being good on the video. I tryed not to make it lag to much.
